# 📊 Netflix Data Analysis Project

This project analyzes the **Netflix Movies and TV Shows** dataset from Kaggle. It provides visual insights into content type trends, genres, countries, and content ratings.

## 📁 Files Included

- `Netflix_Report_Abhishek_Singh.pdf` – Final report with analysis & graphs
- `netflix_titles.csv` – Source dataset
- `graphs/` – All generated visualizations (PNG format)

## 🔍 Key Insights

- Distribution of Movies vs TV Shows
- Content added to Netflix over the years
- Most frequent genres
- Top content-producing countries
- Most common content ratings

## 🛠️ Tools Used

- Python (Pandas, Matplotlib, Seaborn)
- Jupyter Notebook
- FPDF (for PDF report)

